  m_Text: '    In this game, you can control four characters: a rooster, a deer,
    a tiger, or a dog. You run on the road by moving forward, backward, left, or
    right, collecting coins along the way to earn points. You start with 3 health
    points, and hitting obstacles will reduce your health. The game ends when your
    health reaches zero. Your goal is to collect as many coins as possible while
    avoiding dangers and to challenge for higher scores!'
